{"tid":1855614,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我有朋友整左一個AI 極度快速幫你登記功能組別","createTime":"2020-02-01T07:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T21:16:40.000Z","uid":182998,"like":171,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"ec19cf6fc0afa9d6505ade1d084cec91bdf41b95","tid":1855614,"uid":182998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:37:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2020廢除功能組別 立法會真普選</strong></span></span><br />\n但如果未能廢除只要我地有大量選民基礎依然有機會比到壓力政府<br />\n大家連無實權的區議會都希望去投 更何況立法會呢？<br />\n只要我地可以過半 呢個運動絕對可以再行前一步<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Link：</strong><a href=\"https://handyhands.com.hk/fbm.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhandyhands.com.hk%2Ffbm.html&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IokJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=658ae71a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://handyhands.com.hk/fbm.html</a><br />\n因為我地呢個AI chat bot只係幫你了解你應該點先投到票<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所以我地唔會接收到你任何個人資料</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">需要使用Facebook messager 用電話的人請先下載app</span><br />\n<br />\n入教學之前先解答大家的問題<br />\n首先，我地係咩人？<br />\n我地唔係想出名 拎咩光環做咩大台 無背景 無靠山<br />\n原本想整個數碼助理的app出黎但覺得其實可以為呢場運動做d野<br />\n所以想搵個方法等大家唔會咁怕煩而唔登記功能組別<br />\nQ：食屎啦 想拎我地d資料<br />\nA：過程中你唔需要入任何個人資料<br />\nQ：屌 用facebook你咪知道我係邊個？<br />\nA：歡迎用任何假facebook ac再用facebook messager 唔會有任何影響<br />\nQ：On9 咁你咪統計到我地有幾多人係咩組別？<br />\nA：你可以隨便無限次鳩揀 所以如果要統計都唔知點計<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我地真係唔知點先證明到我地係自己友 請大家自己判斷</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">使用教學</span></strong><br />\n1. 按link進入<br />\n2. 開始使用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9qqJW6p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9qqJW6p.jpg&h=16e79324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3. 揀自己從事的行業<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WTCHtdu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWTCHtdu.jpg&h=efa07f76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4. 我是資訊科技界的IT狗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DLgMUUa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDLgMUUa.jpg&h=1033dc1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5. 原來要入協會！？但我未入！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1NdrUUn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1NdrUUn.jpg&h=0b8fcbf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6. 提供網站比你登記 <span style=\"color: red;\">全程無收過你任何個人資料</span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cOy0eVJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcOy0eVJ.jpg&h=20ad8320&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n7. 如果想由頭揀過出番個app向左掃del左個chat再入過link就得<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bshsEnC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbshsEnC.jpg&h=3d8d92ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經整左的功能組別<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">IT，紡織，飲食，工程，會計，建築、測量，醫學，法律，衛生，社福</span></strong></span><br />\n我地會陸續update 請大家幫幫手散出去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CS33Xd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCS33Xd6.jpg&h=e6f7b84a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港 時代革命  </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"58315603af44ce8959df988a6b2b681b81627ef3","tid":1855614,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:38:46.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"b432ea42d2e88c6130b9511aaf7a07376d27aeb3","tid":1855614,"uid":193233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:38:53.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"2784714c39ce5c578791c56fba38d891b1ad8e18","tid":1855614,"uid":182998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:39:12.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b31f0be125ddfd89f6f9f4733eff183aef3032f4","tid":1855614,"uid":76922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:39:15.000Z","msg":"<img 