,{"pid":"cfd2b06500c69a780a78ac658fdfea28936dc00e","tid":1855614,"uid":182998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T22:39:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cbeac8a4072fcf20ba9f7debe99021ea34527e58","tid":1855614,"uid":55055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T23:26:32.000Z","msg":"Thank You!!!"},{"pid":"0ef15c5a89cd3f5edfe8e717f71aee8cf8cf1c22","tid":1855614,"uid":147242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T23:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f50c01f455321c1b2f47b7479f7d0cd7dca74d","tid":1855614,"uid":114434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T23:38:36.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"dbe09f79fb13f836ab3ece8de9898a86b93c30a8","tid":1855614,"uid":337613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec19cf6fc0afa9d6505ade1d084cec91bdf41b95","tid":1855614,"uid":182998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:37:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2020廢除功能組別 立法會真普選</strong></span></span><br />\n但如果未能廢除只要我地有大量選民基礎依然有機會比到壓力政府<br />\n大家連無實權的區議會都希望去投 更何況立法會呢？<br />\n只要我地可以過半 呢個運動絕對可以再行前一步<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Link：</strong><a href=\"https://handyhands.com.hk/fbm.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhandyhands.com.hk%2Ffbm.html&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IokJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=658ae71a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://handyhands.com.hk/fbm.html</a><br />\n因為我地呢個AI chat bot只係幫你了解你應該點先投到票<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所以我地唔會接收到你任何個人資料</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">需要使用Facebook messager 用電話的人請先下載app</span><br />\n<br />\n入教學之前先解答大家的問題<br />\n首先，我地係咩人？<br />\n我地唔係想出名 拎咩光環做咩大台 無背景 無靠山<br />\n原本想整個數碼助理的app出黎但覺得其實可以為呢場運動做d野<br />\n所以想搵個方法等大家唔會咁怕煩而唔登記功能組別<br />\nQ：食屎啦 想拎我地d資料<br />\nA：過程中你唔需要入任何個人資料<br />\nQ：屌 用facebook你咪知道我係邊個？<br />\nA：歡迎用任何假facebook ac再用facebook messager 唔會有任何影響<br />\nQ：On9 咁你咪統計到我地有幾多人係咩組別？<br />\nA：你可以隨便無限次鳩揀 所以如果要統計都唔知點計<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我地真係唔知點先證明到我地係自己友 請大家自己判斷</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">使用教學</span></strong><br />\n1. 按link進入<br />\n2. 開始使用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9qqJW6p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9qqJW6p.jpg&h=16e79324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3. 揀自己從事的行業<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WTCHtdu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWTCHtdu.jpg&h=efa07f76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4. 我是資訊科技界的IT狗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DLgMUUa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDLgMUUa.jpg&h=1033dc1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5. 原來要入協會！？但我未入！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1NdrUUn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1NdrUUn.jpg&h=0b8fcbf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6. 提供網站比你登記 <span style=\"color: red;\">全程無收過你任何個人資料</span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cOy0eVJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcOy0eVJ.jpg&h=20ad8320&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n7. 如果想由頭揀過出番個app向左掃del左個chat再入過link就得<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bshsEnC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbshsEnC.jpg&h=3d8d92ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經整左的功能組別<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">IT，紡織，飲食，工程，會計，建築、測量，醫學，法律，衛生，社福</span></strong></span><br />\n我地會陸續update 請大家幫幫手散出去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CS33Xd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCS33Xd6.jpg&h=e6f7b84a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港 時代革命  </span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T23:40:31.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"656e98e59878477ec60908864f4c6c769d7b2bbc","tid":1855614,"uid":138286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T23:51:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb8fd5585c054e8666fe3cfa2e85c88d42662037","tid":1855614,"uid":134907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T23:58:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0442ab854889d5d523d7e5edbf9478344ca499e4","tid":1855614,"uid":1333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T00:07:39.000Z","msg":"用facebook政府知你幾多人會用<br />\n豬閪百格拎埋黎做Data Analysis"},{"pid":"8ac17b90a7c7b567b07f2602c28bcf5f0997d9b4","tid":1855614,"uid":143183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T00:23:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9ce0e3bbb1f5b9552ddd08b9b9ef49f1a8b2ae99","tid":1855614,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T00:24:25.000Z","msg":"呀"},{"pid":"18c0b8d313b847ddf35036a250157275adceb60f","tid":1855614,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T00:24:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"558026d72fb21c6a17631a2e0bde5bca7e86a4b9","tid":1855614,"uid":197086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T00:26:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00878b3566b8f985d614bd64149be986d693737c","tid":1855614,"uid":28444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T00:29:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"55762d74aca08af64bef4ac0246873ab0c285283","tid":1855614,"uid":244953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T00:30:31.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"cfcc758a23e0e8641598ad8ca49e61d053739d0b","tid":1855614,"uid":31974,"like":0